title: Annie Lennox - Live at The Mermaid Theatre (BBC Radio 2 Concert)
description:
An amazing night when BBC Radio invited Annie Lennox to perform her hits as well as new tracks from her latest album SONGS OF MASS DESTRUCTION, alongside the BBC Orchestra. A unique chance to experience Annie&#039;s songs in orchestral arrangements.
